y":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"李卓人跨區鎅票既報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f0f1f26aef06536162a983294acbd40cd4d91a","tid":863462,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"反中央？你死啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140610/52571277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140610%2F52571277&d=SzeCi%2Frp0vCg6CgE8yKKzzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=01bdb23b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140610%2F52571277&h=6af3c527\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140610/52571277</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">李卓人：不接受中央操控就要站出來</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20140610/large/1402399312_5a40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140610%2Flarge%2F1402399312_5a40.jpg&h=65960d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院白皮書強調中央對香港有全面管治權，支聯會主席、工黨立法會議員李卓人表示，中央經常強調治權，但忘記一國兩制下，中央有責任尊重香港人的民意，而普選是基本法的承諾，「(港人)只係拎返應有的普選權，如果(中央)用咁強硬態度，以我為主，全面霸權，香港人唔服」。他指如港人不接受白皮書，不接受一切以北京意願為主，就要「行出來」，參與本月14日起的毅行爭普選活動。<br />\n<br />\n李卓人認為，中央發表此白皮書，目的是要打壓香港人爭普選的意志，以中央意志為主，「佢想少啲人出來投票，少啲人出來七一遊行、佔中，但壓迫愈大，反抗愈大，香港人係唔受呢一套，你打壓唔到」。他強調，現在是「民意戰京意」，港人要行出來爭取應有權力，不可讓中央完全操控。"},{"pid":"b29add496430a636b544f9f7289590487d9e990e","tid":863462,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6babc3ed3e42b054de2e34888eb4de874cca8e10","tid":863462,"uid":35166,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"李卓人都唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"「支持結束一黨專政」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990a7a0fc843c19582c942a58ac8fe2d212ea649","tid":863462,"uid":156130,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"成班鬼駛唔駛幫晒選舉主任搵証據"},{"pid":"000b8fc47830dc60e1c46aa636fd9a12e0e245f2","tid":863462,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"DQ李卓人 = DQ黎智英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29edbc7100b95841e2efb176dc834975d6624357","tid":863462,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"馮檢基執雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94fd1f60a9d9a24e5d75cf0272a113a9b48419d","tid":863462,"uid":213091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:10:26.000Z","msg":"Dq哂得啦其實仲有咩好選"},{"pid":"af5b31aa5e0831029ead9662bdcfed41d0a2d846","tid":863462,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"選嚟把撚？委任啦"},{"pid":"d113f50300d5e0fffde2d131cb24ce739e410eba","tid":863462,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"一陣SENDF 比CEO OFFICE<br />\n<br />\n想睇下D100班老野會唔會講比人DQ抵死"},{"pid":"21244453be59b72957bb5420262704d3c5401a1f","tid":863462,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/imagecache/w456/column_images/64lei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fw456%2Fcolumn_images%2F64lei.jpg&h=587dc262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n革命黨人李卓人"},{"pid":"01c28c126c5a83d6afa6158c89d433756ade5475","tid":863462,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"快d dq佢"},{"pid":"9b5281fd23a9ee343d50d946973b2cbfc60f8c87","tid":863462,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"同基哥大和解就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046ccac9c95f7711075107de3e179f30b0346085","tid":863462,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:31:34.000Z","msg":"李卓人咁撚溫和共產黨都驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c501d080f9a518d3527f0ab76dbf486125dcb20","tid":863462,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"到時泛民記住集中票源投基哥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c4d22ef5d914d343f0a7c4c5c51b45e37e8fac","tid":863462,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b5281fd23a9ee343d50d946973b2cbfc60f8c87","tid":863462,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"同基哥大和解就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:43:18.000Z","msg":"基哥畀啲骨氣，唔好理班屈鬼仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}